data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET DUE TO NO FAULT OF THE SELLER! 4 bed/3 bath tropical oasis with pool and unattached cottage in highly desirable Fairway Oaks! This all brick and Hardie board siding house sits on oversized wooded lot and is an entertainers dream! Open concept kitchen features quartz countertops, two sinks, stainless steel appliances, and large walk-in butler's pantry. Unattached cottage is 640 sq ft w/ 320 sq ft screened in porch with fireplace and laundry. Cottage features all tile floors, quartz countertops, large ADA tile shower and double French doors leading to private 2 story deck! Additional features include saltwater pool, updated bathrooms, newer HVACs, shiplap accent walls, 40 x 70 garden area, 3 separate storage units, sunroom, and space to host parties for over 200 people! Could be rented out to traveling nurses as it's less than a mile from Candler or Memorial. Perfect for family with senior living at home or anyone wanting separate quarters! NO HOA! NO FLOOD INSURANCE!
